        Selling a Property with Unapproved Structures in Brisbane: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Unapproved decks, sheds, and secondary dwellings are common across Brisbane's inner east. How you handle them before and during a sale matters more than most sellers realise.
      </p>
